{"tid":614684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咩都懶得去做，性格on9，有冇人垃圾過我","createTime":"2018-04-02T17:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T18:40:56.000Z","uid":54596,"like":41,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9900bbffba8722c7245b6e55b9bbc96cc7890025","tid":614684,"uid":54596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"讀完個垃圾HD都2年，22歲就23，<br />\n都係渾渾噩噩咁Hea到而家，工都冇乜點搵，係返過下少少part time，係屋企佔大部分時間。<br />\n<br />\n有好多野都想過做，例如學下有用既技能，或者學下啲唔同方面既興趣<br />\n但得個想字，對呢啲冇deadline既目標，完全冇踏出過一步。<br />\n<br />\n社交方面，我呢啲毒撚性格，但一直對住啲朋友都扮演幽默既人，做小丑角色。<br />\n但我本身好悲觀，有咩野都唔會同人講，因為冇人覺得我會唔開心。<br />\n身邊冇人可以做我傾訴對象，每次我都係做聽人訴苦嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n而且啲朋友個個拍哂拖，得我冇，令我更加覺得自己性格有問題，之後更頹，無限loop。<br />\n<br />\n機會唔係冇，但我一對人有興趣，就會chur爆人，之後嚇走人，所以一直都好憎自己咁on9。<br />\n<br />\n到而家，我已經咩都懶得做，我好唔明點解我個快性格要咁on9，我寧願天生mk仔性格，唔洗理世俗眼光，做乜都自由自在，自己開心就得。"},{"pid":"9fcf6cdc8e597fc62481e8bfb13e98cb794d2ab0","tid":614684,"uid":178574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:40:59.000Z","msg":"咩科HD"},{"pid":"9379879986bdecf97e9fc43f35350102b2a174e0","tid":614684,"uid":54596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩科HD</blockquote><br />\n工程，一條女都冇個啲"},{"pid":"acfdc6cfcc142c402468e2707bb19ac0870ea293","tid":614684,"uid":89955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩科HD</blockquote><br />\n工程，一條女都冇個啲</blockquote><br />\n做野啦死廢青"},{"pid":"b10643e33a61ebf3ccf5bd05ef0bc702bc3e0234","tid":614684,"uid":54596,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩科HD</blockquote><br />\n工程，一條女都冇個啲</blockquote><br />\n做野啦死廢青</blockquote><br />\n連面對返工都冇勇氣，個人生好似冇乜希望咁。"},{"pid":"f39737da76d08e2a390fb6dfc7c670f78dd2cb2e","tid":614684,"uid":162491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"唔死都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e17e1c100d0e88b1bbea7f63ab842221623a968","tid":614684,"uid":54596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f39737da76d08e2a390fb6dfc7c670f78dd2cb2e","tid":614684,"uid":162491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"唔死都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9348fa13a11ab4c5061b2b23e7e7b6c8b5e818b4","tid":614684,"uid":94819,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5b00e3d55f01beb5cd6778321acc7ec6c879160","tid":614684,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"以為係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85a7dd85032ccef6f3c24053808c08cc6f142f8","tid":614684,"uid":149151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b477af6bdfead4208a19862fd0f29d39381cc48","tid":614684,"uid":57058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:11:28.000Z","msg":"好似自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debdb7947489722523e9bf479ed6d351cf12d98a","tid":614684,"uid":16469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"搵方法改啦 on99一世唔撚掂"},{"pid":"2a50f870f46fb53a3ce5d047c164933965c54549","tid":614684,"uid":60342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:13:52.000Z","msg":"工程佬<br />\n<br />\n放心啦<br />\n<br />\n過多6-7年<br />\n<br />\n你都會係一樣，改變唔到<br />\n<br />\n搵樣興趣玩下吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8afcb4e0ccfef537577f2750ceb288639b544b5","tid":614684,"uid":44958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:21:05.000Z","msg":